  <brief_title>Evaluation of a Web-based Virtual Nursing Epilepsy Self-Management Intervention</brief_title>
  <official_title>Evaluation of a Web-based Virtual Nursing Intervention to Support Self-Management Among Adults With Epilepsy: A Preliminary Study</official_title>
