  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this pilot randomized controlled trial is to evaluate a web-based virtual
      nursing intervention (ÉPI-TAVIE) in terms of 1) acceptability and feasibility, and; 2)
      preliminary efficacy.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
